    * SETTINGS - WHEEL SUSPENSION
    * Strength of Wheel Suspension needs to be calculated
    Strength of \WHSU = 20
    Power of \WHSU = 60
    Speed Limit of \WHSU = 20
    MaxSteerAngle of \WHSF = 21
    MaxSteerAngle of \WHSB = 11
}

